- Takes `PointsExtractData` (nullable/undefined) and returns `ProcessedExtractData`
- Returns a default empty structure if data is missing
- Groups transactions by date using `getGroupedTransactionsByDate()`
- Maps grouped data into flat list with labels via `PointsDataGroupedByDayMapper.getMappedData()`
- Catches errors and returns default data on failure

